    <h3>Overview</h3>
      <p>Bull City Food Growlers is a reusable take-out container program that aims
         to reduce waste and cost for local restaurants and improve the quality of
         life for Durhamites.
      </p>
        <p>Bull City Food Growlers are durable and long-lasting
        take-out containers which are 100% reusable. They can be washed and sanitized in commercial dishwashers. They are used in similar sustainable
        container programs across the country.
      </p>
    <h3>How It Works</h3>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Alert participating food establishment that you are a participant in the program</li>
          <li>Authenticate at pick up</li>
          <li>Take food home</li>
          <li>Return container at participating site</li>
          <li>repeat</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
